profile: Greely Sand & Gravel is one of Ottawaâ€™s largest suppliers of mulch, sand, topsoil and stone. We have the best selection and the most delivery options available in the city. GS&G has been a family-run business since 1982 and has earned a reputation as the best landscape supplier in Eastern Ontario.
service_area: We deliver all over Ottawa, which includes central Kanata to central Orleans to Kemptville. Outside of these areas may have ...
products: Greely Sand & Gravel offers a wide variety of landscaping and construction products, including mulch, river rock, sand, stone, and playground material.  Greely offers the best in certified products, including playground mulch, playground sand, playground stone, Hydro Sand, Septic Sand, and CU-Structural Soil. We also offer premium weed barriers, grass seed, polymeric sand, and lawn & garden tools.
services: Greely Sand & Gravel is a leader in innovative services.  We offer deliveries of products by the single product or two different products on our split truck.  Other ways to get deliveries is by our boom truck in cubic yard bags and half cubic yard bags.  Our Mini Roll-off Containers offer customers the chance to get 2 products delivered in the container which they can then rent the container for yard waste or excavation removal.  Our Lawn & Garden Tool Rental Kit offers do-it-yourself homeowners the opportunity to get the job done with all the tools they need.  Greely's DisposaBag is new to Greely's services and allows customers to get rid of Garden Waste, Excavation Waste, and Non-Hazardous Household waste by filling a cubic yard bag and having Greely pick it up.
payment_method: Visa, Master Card, Cash, Personal Cheque and Debit (at landscape depots)
memberships: Landscape Ontario; Composting Council of Canada; CQA; NCHCA; OSSGA; CLAEO; OCA; OSWCA;
